name: Api\Objects\SearchResponse
description: See the fields returned by the search article endpoints.

properties.name: links
properties.description: A list of fields returned by the Search Articles in a Section and Search Articles in a Channel endpoints.

properties.name: meta
properties.description: The value that should be set for the pageToken parameter as well as the parameters that were previously sent to get the next page of results. This field is automatically filled in with the next URL in the links section.
